name: My Soul Whispers and I Fly

metadata.name: The Path
metadata.description:
'Ever since the moment I came into this world,
I was walking from the very beginning.
In a mansion with only two doors.
I'm walking on, day and night' Aşık Veysel

This photo was taken during a funeral ceremony of a Monk at Vipassana Dhura Buddist Center.  In the photo Budist Monks are walking in crowds and rows, showing their respect and gratitude for the funeral.

Location: Phnom Penh /Cambodia (2019)

Photographer: Öykü Tunaboyu

Edition: 1/1

Dimensions: 4035x2690
